arty！”主视觉的超大面板也将出现。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[#hololivesummer2023]主旋律《青春档案》动画MV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YzQCNmk3YYA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/30268-963-7659067889f86019307707e929a26344-1920x1080-1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/30268-963-7659067889f86019307707e929a26344-1920x1080-1-1024x576.jpg"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/30268-963-0bdb917e186f987d4b67b1acc17d2a99-1920x1080-1.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/30268-963-0bdb917e186f987d4b67b1acc17d2a99-1920x1080-1-1024x576.jpg"></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/pastedimage0-47.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/07/pastedimage0-47-1024x576.png"></a></p><p>此外，《Holo Live Summer 2023》主旋律《青春档案》动画MV发布，为夏季量身定制的情境视频在各艺人个人频道连续53天发布。将发售使用浴衣和泳装的原创商品，并在丸井开设快闪店。</p><p>点击此处购买“Holo Live Summer 2023”商品vol.1。<br /> <a href="https://shop.hololivepro.com/collections/all?sort_by=manual&amp;q=%22hololivesummer2023%22" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://shop.hololivepro.com/collections/all?sort_by=manual&amp;q=%22hololivesummer2023%22</a></p><p>点击此处查看特别网站。<br /> <a href="https://hololivesummer2023.hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hololivesummer2023.hololivepro.com/</a></p><h2> Hololive Summer 2023 3DLIVE Splash Party！概述</h2><table><tbody><tr><td>内容</td><td>[第一天]泼水派对！阳光<br />[Day2] 泼水派对！之夜</td></tr><tr><td>活动日期</td><td>[第一天] 8 月 26 日星期六<br />开放时间: 19:30<br />开始: 20:00</p><p> [第二天] 8月27日（周日）<br />开放时间: 19:30<br />开始: 20:00</td></tr><tr><td>演员</td><td>[第一天]<br />时野空/梅尔·夜空/亚希/白神吹雪/夏色祭/凑阿克娅